{{作品名稱|name=''The Book of Henry''|hk=亨利的簿衛戰|tw=亨利之書|equiv-cn=tw}}是一部2017年[[美國|美國]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，由[[柯林·崔佛洛|柯林·崔佛洛]]執導，[[娜歐蜜·華茲|娜歐蜜·華茲]]、[[傑登·里柏赫|傑登·里柏赫]]、[[雅各·特倫布雷|雅各·特倫布雷]]和[[李·佩斯|李·佩斯]]主演<ref>{{cite web |last=Perez |first=Rodrigo |url=http://theplaylist.net/interview-colin-trevorrow-talks-book-henry-going-blockbusters-indie-films-20160505 |title=Interview: Colin Trevorrow Talks ''The Book of Henry'' & Going From Blockbusters to Indie Films Again |website=ThePlaylist.net |date=2016-05-05 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430121800/https://theplaylist.net/interview-colin-trevorrow-talks-book-henry-going-blockbusters-indie-films-20160505/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Gettell |first=Oliver |url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/10/05/book-of-henry-maddie-ziegler-jacob-tremblay-jaeden-lieberher |title=Colin Trevorrow introduces young Book of Henry stars on Twitter |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |date=2015-10-05 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126065512/https://ew.com/article/2015/10/05/book-of-henry-maddie-ziegler-jacob-tremblay-jaeden-lieberher/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主要拍攝於2015年11月完成。電影由[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]發行，並定於2017年6月16日在美國上映。

==劇情==
故事敘述在一個郊區的小城鎮，一名單親母親蘇珊獨力扶養兩名小孩，分別是早熟11歲的男孩亨利和他的弟弟彼得。亨利為了讓鄰居女孩免於繼父的虐待，而自行撰寫了一本拯救她計劃的書。亨利的母親發現了這本書，她決定和彼得將亨利的計劃付諸行動<ref>{{cite web |last1=Anand |first1=Gautam |first2=Amal |last2=Singh |first3=Prabal |last3=Hazarika |url=http://www.thecinemaholic.com/50-most-anticipated-movies-of-2016-part-2/ |website=The Cinemaholic |date=2016-01-20 |access-date=2017-03-31 |title=50 Most Anticipated Movies of 2016 (Part – 2) |archive-date=2016-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415212556/http://www.thecinemaholic.com/50-most-anticipated-movies-of-2016-part-2 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Madison |first=Charles |url=http://www.filmdivider.com/9598/peeking-inside-colin-trevorrows-book-of-henry/ |title=Peeking inside Colin Trevorrow's ''Book of Henry'' |website=FilmDivider.com |date=2015-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403144512/http://www.filmdivider.com/9598/peeking-inside-colin-trevorrows-book-of-henry/ |archive-date=2015-04-03 |access-date=2017-03-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://2paragraphs.com/2016/01/maddie-zieglers-first-movie-the-book-of-henry-with-naomi-watts/ |title=Maddie Ziegler's First Movie ''The Book of Henry'' with Naomi Watts |website=2Paragraphs.com |date=2016-01-05 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2016-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915110626/http://2paragraphs.com/2016/01/maddie-zieglers-first-movie-the-book-of-henry-with-naomi-watts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

