==製作==
===發展===
起初，{{le|格雷格·赫爾維茲|Gregg Hurwitz}}於1998年就已撰寫了《亨利之書》的第一稿劇本。電影被選中成為確定推出的計劃項目，{{le|珍奈特·卡恩|Jenette Kahn}}和{{le|西德尼·凱米爾娛樂|Sidney Kimmel Entertainment}}的{{le|西德尼·凱米爾|Sidney Kimmel}}都已加入擔任監製。西德尼·凱米爾娛樂的一名董事認為，讓[[柯林·崔佛洛|柯林·崔佛洛]]執導將是正確的，儘管崔佛洛先被雇用執導《[[侏羅紀世界|侏羅紀世界]]》。至2015年初，崔佛洛結束《侏羅紀世界》的工作後，他回來繼續進行《亨利之書》的製作計劃<ref>{{cite web |last=Le |first=D. Dona |url=http://www.harvardwood.org/q_a_hurwitz |title=Exclusive Q&A with Gregg Hurwitz '95 (''Orphan X'', ''The Book of Henry'') |website=Harvardwood |date=2016-01-01 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108092012/https://www.harvardwood.org/q_a_hurwitz |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last1=Kit |first1=Borys |title='Jurassic World' Director Colin Trevorrow Tackling 'Book of Henry' |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-world-director-colin-trevorrow-785370 |accessdate=2015-04-05 |publisher=hollywoodreporter.com |date=2015-03-30 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403180933/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/jurassic-world-director-colin-trevorrow-785370 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。西德尼·凱米爾娛樂和Double Nickel Entertainment將合作並共同出資電影；電影的監製包括凱米爾、珍奈特·卡恩和亞當·里士曼<ref name="thewrap">{{cite news |last1=Sneider |first1=Jeff |title=''Jurassic World's'' Colin Trevorrow to Direct ''Book of Henry'' for Sidney Kimmel |url=http://www.thewrap.com/jurassic-worlds-colin-trevorrow-to-direct-book-of-henry-for-sidney-kimmel/ |accessdate=2015-04-05 |work=thewrap |date=2015-03-30 |archive-date=2021-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210113081411/https://www.thewrap.com/jurassic-worlds-colin-trevorrow-to-direct-book-of-henry-for-sidney-kimmel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]則獲得了電影在全球的發行權<ref>{{cite news |last1=Kroll |first1=Justin |title=Jacob Tremblay, Jaeden Lieberher to Co-Star in Colin Trevorrow's ''Book of Henry'' |url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/jacob-tremblay-jaeden-lieberher-book-of-henry-colin-trevorrow-1201573908 |website=Variety.com |date=2015-08-19 |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108121046/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/jacob-tremblay-jaeden-lieberher-book-of-henry-colin-trevorrow-1201573908/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===拍攝===
[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2015年9月在[[紐約市|紐約市]]及其周邊地區開始進行<ref name=Manskar/><ref name="Oct2015CS">{{cite news |last1=Evry |first1=Max |title=Jurassic World Director Colin Trevorrow's The Book of Henry Begins Filming |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/619617-jurassic-world-director-colin-trevorrows-the-book-of-henry-begins-filming |date=2015-10-05 |work=comingsoon.net |accessdate=2017-06-19 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108115443/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/619617-jurassic-world-director-colin-trevorrows-the-book-of-henry-begins-filming |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Book of Henry Filming – Update {{!}} Village of South Nyack |url=http://southnyack.ny.gov/book-of-henry-filming-update/ |website=southnyack.ny.gov |accessdate=2015-09-13 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020004611/http://southnyack.ny.gov/book-of-henry-filming-update/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Ferraro |first=Tom |url=http://theislandnow.com/opinions-100/the-day-the-circus-came-to-williston-park/ |title=Our Town: The day the circus came to Williston Park |website=The Island Now |date=2015-09-12 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603144306/https://theislandnow.com/opinions-100/the-day-the-circus-came-to-williston-park/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於11月結束<ref name="Lowe">{{cite web |last=Lowe |first=Kinsey |url=http://deadline.com/2015/11/colin-trevorrow-the-book-of-henry-wraps-nyc-1201633764/ |title=Colin Trevorrow Tweets ''The Book Of Henry'' has Wrapped Filming |website=Deadline.com |date=2015-09-21 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310141332/http://deadline.com/2015/11/colin-trevorrow-the-book-of-henry-wraps-nyc-1201633764/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影的音樂是由[[麥可·吉亞奇諾|麥可·吉亞奇諾]]負責<ref>{{cite web |url=http://filmmusicreporter.com/2016/02/16/michael-giacchino-to-score-colin-trevorrows-the-book-of-henry/ |title=Michael Giacchino to Score Colin Trevorrow's ''The Book of Henry'' |website=FilmMusicReporter.com |date=2016-02-16 |access-date=2017-03-31 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125134911/http://filmmusicreporter.com/2016/02/16/michael-giacchino-to-score-colin-trevorrows-the-book-of-henry/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[史蒂薇·妮克絲|史蒂薇·妮克絲]]則在電影中唱了一首新歌<ref>Vulpo, Mike. [http://www.eonline.com/news/860645/stevie-nicks-releases-new-song-for-the-book-of-henry-listen-to-your-hand-i-will-never-let-it-go-now "Stevie Nicks Releases New Song for The Book of Henry: Listen to 'Your Hand I Will Never Let It Go' Now"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eonline.com/news/860645/stevie-nicks-releases-new-song-for-the-book-of-henry-listen-to-your-hand-i-will-never-let-it-go-now |date=20201111222520 }}, Eonline.com, 2017-06-13</ref>。

